{"tid":264612,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Computex 2017：AMD確認發佈旗艦顯卡、Ryzen APU","createTime":"2017-05-31T03:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T21:28:34.000Z","uid":78764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd272aca60f3aff8072bac5ba34e32f5f8e9ebc","tid":264612,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"今天凌晨AMD公開宣佈，他們將在北京時間5月31日早上10點舉辦技術大會，毫無疑問其中一個主角是全新的Vega遊戲顯卡。<br />\n根據目前曝光的情況看，AMD準備的Radeon RX Vega Frontier Edition價格預計599美元，其配備了64個計算單元(4096個流處理器)，單精度浮點性能12.5TFlops，半精度25TFlops，搭配16GB HBM2顯存，帶寬480GB/s，可以支持8K顯示輸出。<br />\n性能殘暴的AMD Vega遊戲卡終於要來了！<br />\n此外，以性能來對比的話，Radeon Vega Frontier Edition能夠戰勝NVIDIA的前任專業卡皇Tesla P100，但相比最新的Tesla V100來說還有比較明顯的差距。<br />\n<br />\n既然是技術大會，除了新顯卡外，據說還會展示基於Zen和Vega架構的新一代APU。之前，SiSoftware數據庫曝光Ryzen APU的核心參數，確認是4核8線程CPU核心，GPU則是11組CU單元，704個流處理器單元，不過有點意外的是GPU搭配了3GB DDR3。<br />\n<br />\n轉自大陸網<br />\n<br />\n利伸：等緊Ryzen APU"},{"pid":"2859834798c96374e69c6cc6a15ec1d4dbb1404b","tid":264612,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"AMD Computex Livestream 2017<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WK9z6NO1qyU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWK9z6NO1qyU&d=Jlyqv5s1JpooMF7Os7siI%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8d15af70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WK9z6NO1qyU</a>"},{"pid":"41d3d91ba9545fb0fd47725980f548551d6dfffb","tid":264612,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"屌無料到, 得mobile apu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459d7a933cd5e209b4f87fbc18c3df480da84f49","tid":264612,"uid":38486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌無料到, 得mobile apu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/n